Package com.apw.gpu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlackWhiteRasterKernel
    The MonochromeRasterKernel subclass describes a Kernel that converts a bayer rgb byte array into a black and white bayer byte array.
    BWToRGBKernel
    The BWToRGBKernel subclass describes a Kernel that creates a monochromatic raw rgb pixel array from a black and white bayer rgb array
    ImageProcessing  
    MonochromeRasterKernel
    The MonochromeRasterKernel subclass describes a Kernel that converts a bayer rgb byte array into a monochromatic bayer byte array.
    MonoToRGBKernel
    The MonoToRGBKernel subclass describes a Kernel that creates a raw rgb pixel array from a monochromatic bayer rgb byte array
    RGBRasterKernel
    The RGBRasterKernel subclass describes a Kernel that converts a bayer rgb byte array into an rgb raster of the same array.
    SimpleColorRasterKernel
    The MonochromeRasterKernel subclass describes a Kernel that creates a simple color raster from a bayer rgb byte array.
    SimpleToRGBKernel
    The SimpleToRGBKernel subclass describes a Kernel that creates a simple 5 color raw rgb pixel array from a simple 5 color raster of bayer rgb array The raster is comprised of RED, GREEN, BLUE, WHITE, and GREY color codes ranging from 0 to 5.
